hopobject.body: What university do you go to? arctic zero seasonal flavors Clearly the formula is working – the app’s success has been meteoric. In less than a year, they claim to have made 75 million matches, 50 million of which have culminated in engagements – speedy work. There have been some inevitable teething problems around security, but there’s no denying that the app is compelling in its simplicity – it’s Top Trumps meets Candy Crush meets Cilla Black, and entirely addictive.
